                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p35q4s610/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">4</p>\n            <p>if there were more or not, he asked me<lb/> if I had had “Halitza”? I replied\n                “Doctor<lb/> you know that is not done any more at<lb/> home” I cannot help it “he\n                said” a<lb/> man named <persName>Ephraim</persName> says he was at school<lb/> with\n                a Brother of your husband's 17 years<lb/> ago, a Trustee meeting has been\n                held—the<lb/> Trustees leave it to me, and I cannot<lb/> marry you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You may imagine my feelings<lb/> Revd. Sir, I had been in\n                    <placeName>California</placeName><lb/> nearly 10 years, had been a widow 7,<lb/>\n                had shown a good example and<lb/> felt dreadfully aggrieved to be so served<lb/> at\n                the last moment. <persName>Mr. P.</persName> said “never<lb/> mind we will go to a\n                Magistrate”<lb/> I replied no—I am very angry<lb/> now, in an hour I shall be more\n                com-<lb/>-posed, I will go round to <persName>Dr. Henry</persName><lb/> and ask him\n                these questions, if he<lb/> answers me satisfactorily we will marry—<lb/>if not, we\n                part. I will never see you<lb/> again—if you please you may</p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_20_1.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 20 No. 1 pages 15 through 19. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p35q4s610/canvas/p4"
                }
              ]
